OL,5,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FThe traffic cops of north
OL,7,     FYorkshire are back, and in this
OL,8,     Fepisode drug drivers are
OL,9,     Fresponsible for a number of highly
OL,10,     Fdangerous incidents. Hosted by
OL,11,     FJamie Theakston.
OL,12,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,13,     FFifteen miles south of York, a
OL,14,     Fprolific car thief crashes and
OL,15,     Frolls a stolen car at over 100mph.
OL,16,     FIn Harrogate, the hunt for a
OL,17,     Fdisqualified driver leads to a
OL,18,     Fhigh-speed pursuit.
