OL,12,     FPresenters Rick Edwards and Ortis
OL,13,     FDelay are out with the police
OL,14,     Finterceptors as they tackle the
OL,15,     Fdifficult night shift.
OL,16,G1600 Police Interceptors
OL,17,     FIn this special episode, the
OL,18,     Finterceptor's take on the young
OL,19,     Fand reckless who cause carnage on
