OL,5,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FThis week at the Hall Green Health
OL,7,     FCentre, the doctors work to get to
OL,8,     Fthe bottom of various conditions.
OL,9,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,10,     FDr Julian Humphrey treats one
OL,11,     Fpatient with a aortic dissection,
OL,12,     Fand another with a regularly
OL,13,     Fdislocated shoulder. Documentary
OL,14,     Fseries filmed inside Barnsley
OL,15,     Fcasualty department.
OL,16,G2100 999: Critical Condition
OL,17,     FHaving plummeted 15 feet onto
OL,18,     Fconcrete, Michael is rushed into
OL,19,     Fresus with a significant
OL,20,     Flaceration to his head. And a
OL,21,     Fdriver has a crushed leg after
OL,22,     Fbeing run over by his own van.
