OL,5,G2200 A&E After Dark
OL,6,     FA patient brought into A&E by
OL,7,     Fpolice claims to have swallowed
OL,8,     Fdrugs, but he refuses to
OL,9,     Fco-operate with staff, putting the
OL,10,     FNHS under further pressure.
OL,11,G2300 The Surgeon
OL,12,     FWe follow consultant brain surgeon
OL,13,     FOmar Pathmanaban as he tackles a
OL,14,     Frare tumour that could be fatal,
OL,15,     Fand also a complex and demanding
OL,16,     Fprocedure requiring surgery via
OL,17,     Fthe nose. (Ep3/4)
