OL,5,G0000 Skin A&E
OL,6,     FDr Adil Sheraz removes a giant
OL,7,     Flipoma from a patient's back,
OL,8,     Fwhile Dr Toby Nelson tackles 13
OL,9,     Flipomas on a single patient, and
